# ─── Vercel deploy ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# In the Vercel dashboard: Project → Settings → Environment Variables.
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL — canonical site URL for metadata, sitemap, robots.
#   Production example: https://sameh-bakleh-portfolio.vercel.app
#   Set for Production only so Preview can use VERCEL_URL.
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_SITE_VERIFICATION — Google Search Console verification token.
#   After adding your site in Search Console, paste the content value from the HTML tag.
#
# VERCEL_URL — set by Vercel; do not add manually.
#
# Contact is mailto-only — no API keys.
